---
title: "{{ title }}"
slug: "{{ slug }}"
date: {{ date }}
series: "{{ series }}"
chapter: "{{ chapter }}"
article_variant: "spoiler"
{% if tags %}
tags:
{% for tag in tags %}
  - "{{ tag }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
tags: []
{% endif %}
draft: {{ draft | lower }}
description: "{{ description }}"
affiliate_ids:
  amazon: "{{ affiliate_ids.amazon }}"
  rakuten: "{{ affiliate_ids.rakuten }}"
{% if affiliate_ids.others %}
  others:
{% for other in affiliate_ids.others %}
    - name: "{{ other.name }}"
      url: "{{ other.url }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
  others: []
{% endif %}
disclaimer: "{{ disclaimer }}"
{% if images %}
images:
{% for image in images %}
  - "{{ image }}"
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
images: []
{% endif %}
---
{{ intro }}

> **{{ spoiler_notice | default("本記事は最新話までのネタバレを含みます。") }}**

{% if hero_image %}
![{{ hero_image.alt }}]({{ hero_image.url }})
<small>Photo by <a href="{{ hero_image.photographer_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ hero_image.photographer }}</a> on <a href="{{ hero_image.pexels_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pexels</a></small>
{% endif %}

## 第{{ chapter_label }}のあらすじ（ざっくり）
{% for point in summary_points %}
- {{ point }}
{% endfor %}

{{ "{{< spoiler >}}" }}
## 第{{ chapter_label }} 詳細ネタバレ（時系列で詳しく）
{{ spoiler.synopsis }}

## 考察・伏線・キャラの心情変化
{% for item in spoiler.foreshadowings %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

## 今後の展開予想（あくまで予想）
{% for item in spoiler.predictions %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
{{ "{{< /spoiler >}}" }}

## 用語集（今回追加・更新分）
{% if glossary_updates %}
{% for term in glossary_updates %}
- **{{ term.term }}**{% if term.reading %}（{{ term.reading }}）{% endif %}: {{ term.description }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
- 今回は既存用語の補足のみでした。
{% endif %}

## 参考リンク（すべて公式）
{% for link in reference_links %}
- [{{ link.label }}]({{ link.url }})
{% endfor %}
